text: Hubert Alexander Ingraham (born 4 August 1947) is a Bahamian politician. He was Prime Minister of the Bahamas from August 1992 to May 2002 and again from May 2007 to May 2012. He is a member of the Free National Movement Party (FNM).Krystel Rolle, "Ingraham resigns" , The Nassau Guardian, 8 May 2012. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:Prime ministers of the Bahamas
